<rss version="2.0" xmlns:content="http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/" xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" xmlns:ss="http://contenthub.aol.com/slideshow/"><channel><title><![CDATA[Engadget is a web magazine with obsessive daily coverage of everything new in gadgets and consumer electronics]]></title><link/> https://www.engadget.com/ <description><![CDATA[Engadget is a web magazine with obsessive daily coverage of everything new in gadgets and consumer electronics]]></description><language> en-US</language><copyright>版权所有雅虎 2023</copyright><pubDate> Tue, 11 Jul 2023 16:00:53 +0000</pubDate><generator>雅虎 http://yahoo.com </generator><item><title><![CDATA[Anthropic releases Claude 2, a more capable, less gullible AI chatbot]]></title><description type="html"><![CDATA[<p>就在 Anthropic 推出其开源 ChatGPT 竞争对手 Claude 五个月后，该公司又推出了<a data-i13n="cpos:1;pos:1" href="https://www.anthropic.com/index/claude-2"><ins>更新版本</ins></a>，承诺更长的答案、更详细的推理、更少的幻觉以及总体上更好的性能。目前，该校在 GRE 阅读和写作考试中的得分也位于研究生院申请者的 90% 之内。 </p><div id="9a5e0afd3b0241cab4e089ec3276d6bd"><div style="left:0;width:100%;height:0;position:relative;padding-bottom:56.338%;"><iframe src="//dk79lclgtez2i.cloudfront.net/2aigQmr" style="top:0;left:0;width:100%;height:100%;position:absolute;border:0;" allowfullscreen="" scrolling="no"></iframe></div></div><p>更新版本 Claude 2<a data-i13n="cpos:2;pos:1" href="https://claude.ai/login"><ins>现已可供美国和英国用户使用</ins></a>。它<a data-i13n="cpos:3;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/anthropic-says-its-claude-ai-can-now-read-a-whole-book-in-under-a-minute-120114018.html"><ins>现在可以处理</ins></a>多达 100,000 个令牌，即大约 75,000 个单词，或者用户可以让 Claude 消化和分析的几百页文档，大大高于之前版本的 9,000 个令牌限制。在人工智能中，令牌是你的输入提示被分解成的碎片，以便模型可以更容易地处理它们——因此克劳德有能力“消化”用户数据。</p><span id="end-legacy-contents"></span><p>这种能力的增强也将转化为更长、更细致的响应。<a data-i13n="cpos:4;pos:1" href="https://www.anthropic.com/index/claude-2"><ins>该公司宣布，</ins></a> Claude 2 甚至能够生成“最多数千个代币”的短篇小说。其编码能力也有所提高，在<a data-i13n="cpos:5;pos:1" href="https://github.com/openai/human-eval">Codex HumanEval</a>基准测试中的得分从 56% 上升至 71.2%。</p><p>克劳德“ <a data-i13n="cpos:6;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/anthropic-explains-how-its-constitutional-ai-girds-claude-against-adversarial-inputs-160008153.html"><ins>宪法人工智能</ins></a>”系统已经受到<a data-i13n="cpos:7;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/anthropics-claude-ai-is-guided-by-10-secret-foundational-pillars-of-fairness-193058471.html"><ins>10 项公平和自治秘密“基础”原则的</ins></a>指导。自第一个版本发布以来，红队进行了广泛的测试，使克劳德 2 成为一个情绪更加稳定、更难以愚弄 AI 的人。据报道，与其前身 Claude 2 相比，“与 Claude 1.3 相比，提供无害响应的能力提高了 2 倍”，该公司在声明中称。如果您已经订阅了 Claude 1.3 API，这是个好消息，您将自动转至 Claude 2，无需额外付费。</p>本文最初发表在 Engadget 上：https://www.engadget.com/anthropic-releases-claude-2-a-more-capable-less-gullible-ai-chatbot-160053168.html?src=rss]]>; </description><link/><![CDATA[https://www.engadget.com/anthropic-releases-claude-2-a-more-capable-less-gullible-ai-chatbot-160053168.html?src=rss]]><source_id> engadget_479</source_id><guid ispermalink="false"> 8ea284f2-3582-4cba-9640-0d975abfb56d</guid><dc:creator>安德鲁·塔兰托拉</dc:creator><source/><![CDATA[Engadget]]><dc:publisher>恩杰特</dc:publisher><dc:rightsholder>恩杰特</dc:rightsholder><pubDate>Tue, 11 Jul 2023 16:00:53 +0000</pubDate><ingested> 1689090965</ingested><modified> 2023-07-11T15:56:09+00:00 </modified><category><![CDATA[site|engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[provider_name|Engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[region|US]]></category><category><![CDATA[language|en-US]]></category><category><![CDATA[author_name|Andrew Tarantola]]></category><media:content height="4000" medium="image" url="https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2023-06/b7477c20-0597-11ee-bbff-7bf54c39e0e1" width="8000"><media:keywords>标题</media:keywords><media:media_html><![CDATA[ ]]></media:media_html><dc:identifier><![CDATA[1]]></dc:identifier><media:credit><![CDATA[ ]]></media:credit><media:description><![CDATA[ ]]></media:description><media:title><![CDATA[ ]]></media:title></media:content><me