erN:Amazon;elmt:;cpos:3;pos:1" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;custData=eyJzb3VyY2VOYW1lIjoiV2ViLURlc2t0b3AtVmVyaXpvbiIsInN0b3JlSWQiOiI2NmVhNTY3YS1jOTg3LTRjMmUtYTJmZi0wMjkwNGVmZGU2ZWEiLCJsYW5kaW5nVXJsIjoiaHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuYW1hem9uLmNvbS9kcC9CMEJXRlNGRDdQP3RhZz1nZGd0MGMtcC1vLTE4YS0yMCIsImNvbnRlbnRVdWlkIjoiMjM3OGNjMjItMjE4ZC00NmIwLWIwOTEtODA5ZDlkODY0NzZmIn0&amp;signature=AQAAAecfQEa29xZLo30hKbSNR3xgCuDsauYe9icE7Z6yxstG&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2Fdp%2FB0BWFSFD7P" class="rapid-with-clickid">新的 S95C</a> 。后者支持更快的 144Hz 刷新率，并通过外部盒子运行其端口，这使得设计更薄。其他<a data-i13n="cpos:4;pos:1" href="https://www.rtings.com/tv/reviews/samsung/s95c-oled">评论家</a><a data-i13n="cpos:5;pos:1" href="https://reviewed.usatoday.com/televisions/features/samsung-s95b-vs-samsung-s95c-which-should-you-buy">说它</a>也可以变得更亮一点。但目前 S95 55 英寸和 65 英寸型号的售价分别为<a data-i13n="elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Amazon;elmt:;cpos:6;pos:1" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;custData=eyJzb3VyY2VOYW1lIjoiV2ViLURlc2t0b3AtVmVyaXpvbiIsInN0b3JlSWQiOiI2NmVhNTY3YS1jOTg3LTRjMmUtYTJmZi0wMjkwNGVmZGU2ZWEiLCJsYW5kaW5nVXJsIjoiaHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuYW1hem9uLmNvbS9kcC9CMEJXRlNGRDdQP3RhZz1nZGd0MGMtcC1vLTE4YS0yMCIsImNvbnRlbnRVdWlkIjoiMjM3OGNjMjItMjE4ZC00NmIwLWIwOTEtODA5ZDlkODY0NzZmIn0&amp;signature=AQAAAecfQEa29xZLo30hKbSNR3xgCuDsauYe9icE7Z6yxstG&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2Fdp%2FB0BWFSFD7P" class="rapid-with-clickid">2,298 美元</a>和<a data-i13n="elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Amazon;elmt:;cpos:7;pos:1" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;custData=eyJzb3VyY2VOYW1lIjoiV2ViLURlc2t0b3AtVmVyaXpvbiIsInN0b3JlSWQiOiI2NmVhNTY3YS1jOTg3LTRjMmUtYTJmZi0wMjkwNGVmZGU2ZWEiLCJsYW5kaW5nVXJsIjoiaHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuYW1hem9uLmNvbS9kcC9CMEJXRlQyNjJQP3RhZz1nZGd0MGMtcC1vLTE4YS0yMCIsImNvbnRlbnRVdWlkIjoiMjM3OGNjMjItMjE4ZC00NmIwLWIwOTEtODA5ZDlkODY0NzZmIn0&amp;signature=AQAAAYW3kaXb_SVCRKhies2qJqwCF3DnHfGT0HkhsIk3HbnO&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2Fdp%2FB0BWFT262P" class="rapid-with-clickid">2,998 美元</a>，而且其升级似乎不足以证明对大多数人来说额外的成本是合理的。如果您正在市场上购买高端电视，那么 S95B 在有货的情况下应该会保持更好的价值。</p><h2> LG C2 </h2><p><core-commerce id="77e7af04a0964c1790294ea37b0abb82" data-type="product-list"></core-commerce></p><p>对于（相对）更实惠的 OLED 电视， <a data-i13n="elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Amazon;elmt:;cpos:8;pos:1" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;custData=eyJzb3VyY2VOYW1lIjoiV2ViLURlc2t0b3AtVmVyaXpvbiIsInN0b3JlSWQiOiI2NmVhNTY3YS1jOTg3LTRjMmUtYTJmZi0wMjkwNGVmZGU2ZWEiLCJsYW5kaW5nVXJsIjoiaHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuYW1hem9uLmNvbS9kcC9CMDlSTUxMSlBYP3RhZz1nZGd0MGMtcC1vLTE4YS0yMCIsImNvbnRlbnRVdWlkIjoiMjM3OGNjMjItMjE4ZC00NmIwLWIwOTEtODA5ZDlkODY0NzZmIn0&amp;signature=AQAAAaNqXKfs-hTJzTEevQNkeUwYbYKKDFpYJKrW-h1mSaGT&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2Fdp%2FB09RMLLJPX" class="rapid-with-clickid">LG C2</a> 55 英寸型号的价格降至 1,097 美元， <a data-i13n="elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Amazon;elmt:;cpos:9;pos:1" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;&amp;signature=AQAAARf2icum9QS3U4AnvyKAAZbPXx6rWhgZGCHFFQmyjdrn&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2Fgp%2Fproduct%2FB09RMRNSBF%2Fref%3Dox_sc_act_title_1" data-demonetize-referrer="https://www.amazon.com/gp/product/B09RMRNSBF/ref=ox_sc_act_title_1?smid=ATVPDKIKX0DER&amp;psc=1" class="rapid-with-clickid">65 英寸型号</a>的价格为 1,496 美元， <a data-i13n="elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Amazon;elmt:;cpos:10;pos:1" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;custData=eyJzb3VyY2VOYW1lIjoiV2ViLURlc2t0b3AtVmVyaXpvbiIsInN0b3JlSWQiOiI2NmVhNTY3YS1jOTg3LTRjMmUtYTJmZi0wMjkwNGVmZGU2ZWEiLCJsYW5kaW5nVXJsIjoiaHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuYW1hem9uLmNvbS9kcC9CMDlSTUZaWlBYP3RhZz1nZGd0MGMtcC1vLTE4YS0yMCIsImNvbnRlbnRVdWlkIjoiMjM3OGNjMjItMjE4ZC00NmIwLWIwOTEtODA5ZDlkODY0NzZmIn0&amp;signature=AQAAAV-E5fnuQeJGD-wHzQgYwFv1G9S6I-eLQpA7pgbbhmZS&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2Fdp%2FB09RMFZZPX" data-demonetize-referrer="https://www.amazon.com/dp/B09RMFZZPX?th=1" class="rapid-with-clickid">42 英寸型号的</a>价格为 797 美元。这些都不是历史最低点，但均比各自的市场价格低约 140 美元。 C2 无法与三星 S95B 等 QD-OLED 设备的亮度和色彩范围相媲美，但它仍然提供出色的对比度、深黑层次和宽视角。它有四个 HDMI 2.1 端口，可以在 120Hz 下播放 4K，支持<a data-i13n="cpos:12;pos:1" href="https://www.hdmi.org/spec21sub/variablerefreshrate">VRR</a>和<a data-i13n="cpos:13;pos:1" href="https://www.hdmi.org/spec21sub/autolowlatencymode">ALLM</a>等<a data-i13n="cpos:11;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/best-tvs-for-gaming-180033983.html">游戏友好功能</a>，并且尺寸范围比 S95B 更广泛。它也适用于所有主要的 HDR 格式，包括杜比视界。只是在明亮的房间里不太理想。</p><p> LG 已于 2023 年推出了<a data-i13n="elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Amazon;elmt:;cpos:14;pos:1" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;custData=eyJzb3VyY2VOYW1lIjoiV2ViLURlc2t0b3AtVmVyaXpvbiIsInN0b3JlSWQiOiI2NmVhNTY3YS1jOTg3LTRjMmUtYTJmZi0wMjkwNGVmZGU2ZWEiLCJsYW5kaW5nVXJsIjoiaHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuYW1hem9uLmNvbS9kcC9CMEJWWEY3MkhWLz90YWc9Z2RndDBjLXAtby0xOGEtMjAiLCJjb250ZW50VXVpZCI6IjIzNzhjYzIyLTIxOGQtNDZiMC1iMDkxLTgwOWQ5ZDg2NDc2ZiJ9&amp;signature=AQAAAQ1-utsrmfGz8DzugBTdMXMDjKTF_k6B3Q2hru6vc2Vq&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2Fdp%2FB0BVXF72HV%2F" class="rapid-with-clickid">新的 C3 型号</a>，但价格更高，而且<a data-i13n="cpos:15;pos:1" href=