ViLURlc2t0b3AtVmVyaXpvbiIsInN0b3JlSWQiOiI2NmVhNTY3YS1jOTg3LTRjMmUtYTJmZi0wMjkwNGVmZGU2ZWEiLCJsYW5kaW5nVXJsIjoiaHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuYW1hem9uLmNvbS9kcC9CMDlXRzcyNjJYP3RhZz1nZGd0MGMtcC1vLTE4YS0yMCIsImNvbnRlbnRVdWlkIjoiMjM3OGNjMjItMjE4ZC00NmIwLWIwOTEtODA5ZDlkODY0NzZmIn0&amp;signature=AQAAAb6Yfkop8PDFAV5i692HfHm8R4KjAnmoh_oz-PaDSufe&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2Fdp%2FB09WG7262X" class="rapid-with-clickid">43 英寸版本的</a>历史最低价<em>为</em>898 美元。 QN90B 是一款液晶电视，因此它无法提供 OLED 面板近乎完美的黑色和超宽视角，但它可以变得更加明亮， <a data-i13n="cpos:27;pos:1" href="https://www.cnet.com/tech/home-entertainment/samsung-qn90b-review-this-qled-tv-from-the-futures-so-bright/">评论</a><a data-i13n="cpos:28;pos:1" href="https://www.nytimes.com/wirecutter/reviews/best-lcd-led-tv/">称</a><a data-i13n="cpos:29;pos:1" href="https://reviewed.usatoday.com/televisions/content/samsung-qn90b-neo-qled-tv-review">它</a>比大多数非 OLED 电视<a data-i13n="cpos:30;pos:1" href="https://www.rtings.com/tv/reviews/samsung/qn90b-qled">提供</a>更好的对比度，这要归功于它的Mini LED背光。仍然没有杜比视界，但它为您提供了四个完整的 HDMI 2.1 端口、4K/120Hz 支持和多种类型的 VRR。如果您想在受眩光困扰的房间购买一台高端电视，那么这是一个不错的选择。</p><p> <a data-i13n="elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Amazon;elmt:;cpos:31;pos:1" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;custData=eyJzb3VyY2VOYW1lIjoiV2ViLURlc2t0b3AtVmVyaXpvbiIsInN0b3JlSWQiOiI2NmVhNTY3YS1jOTg3LTRjMmUtYTJmZi0wMjkwNGVmZGU2ZWEiLCJsYW5kaW5nVXJsIjoiaHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuYW1hem9uLmNvbS9kcC9CMEJUVFZMNDE5P3RhZz1nZGd0MGMtcC1vLTE4YS0yMCIsImNvbnRlbnRVdWlkIjoiMjM3OGNjMjItMjE4ZC00NmIwLWIwOTEtODA5ZDlkODY0NzZmIn0&amp;signature=AQAAASnQbgq-tw_G7_yREolLDaK9JOMk3zko5qsDu-k2qXqO&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2Fdp%2FB0BTTVL419" class="rapid-with-clickid">新款 QN90C</a>已推出，但价格更高，因此，现在购买去年的套装仍然是更好的选择。如果您选择 43 英寸型号，请注意，它的可视角度比较大型号更差，但也支持更快的 144Hz 刷新率。如果您想要一台可以兼作游戏电脑显示器的电视，那么该功能应该很有用。</p><h2>三星 The Frame 电视</h2><p><core-commerce id="216e2497634b4550ae31ed60a9c28e46" data-type="product-list"></core-commerce></p><p>三星 55 英寸<a data-i13n="elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Amazon;elmt:;cpos:32;pos:1" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;custData=eyJzb3VyY2VOYW1lIjoiV2ViLURlc2t0b3AtVmVyaXpvbiIsInN0b3JlSWQiOiI2NmVhNTY3YS1jOTg3LTRjMmUtYTJmZi0wMjkwNGVmZGU2ZWEiLCJsYW5kaW5nVXJsIjoiaHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuYW1hem9uLmNvbS9kcC9CMDlWQ1ZHSDdCP3RhZz1nZGd0MGMtcC1vLTE4YS0yMCIsImNvbnRlbnRVdWlkIjoiMjM3OGNjMjItMjE4ZC00NmIwLWIwOTEtODA5ZDlkODY0NzZmIn0&amp;signature=AQAAAZvofY705Rsi482DL31XUn3XEhmA_N_09j28o6SHUG5C&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2Fdp%2FB09VCVGH7B" class="rapid-with-clickid">The Frame 电视</a>降至 988 美元，创下新低，比一般市场价格低约 450 美元。 The Frame 是一款适合那些愿意牺牲一些图像质量来换取优雅美感的人的电视，因为它的设计看起来就像一件可以挂在墙上的艺术品。当您不观看某些内容时，您可以用它来显示艺术品和照片。其中一些作品包含在内，而其他作品则通过<a data-i13n="elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Samsung Electronics;elmt:;cpos:33;pos:1" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=f85e63cd-e13c-4f9d-991c-9fbaadede3ac&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Samsung+Electronics&amp;&amp;signature=AQAAAW6bIUqHB2ldP4IjbBhBlxE7I2w88jfukKvngbg58cAy&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.samsung.com%2Fus%2Ftelevisions-home-theater%2Ftvs%2Fthe-frame%2Fdigital-art-store%2F" class="rapid-with-clickid">订阅</a>出售。 Frame 的 QLED 面板缺乏局部调光，因此其对比度和 HDR 性能无法真正与同价位的最佳选择竞争。它也只有一个 HDMI 2.1 端口。但图像仍然很差，而且它的设计很好地融入墙壁，正如<a data-i13n="cpos:34;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/samsung-the-frame-tv-irl-153546368.html">我们之前声称的</a>那样。</p><h2>海信U8H </h2><p><core-commerce id="51978c6b5f4b4d3aa30d85c3ccaea01c" data-type="product-list"></core-commerce></p><p>对于那些预算紧张的人来说， <a data-i13n="elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Amazon;elmt:;cpos:35;pos:1" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-lin