Pods 类似，并且无线范围得到了改善。</p><h2> AirPods Max </h2><p><core-commerce id="ebb8d79a123d417484f970120a32d52d" data-type="product-list"></core-commerce></p><p>今年 Prime Day 期间，高端<a data-i13n="elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Amazon;elmt:;cpos:8;pos:1" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;custData=eyJzb3VyY2VOYW1lIjoiV2ViLURlc2t0b3AtVmVyaXpvbiIsInN0b3JlSWQiOiI2NmVhNTY3YS1jOTg3LTRjMmUtYTJmZi0wMjkwNGVmZGU2ZWEiLCJsYW5kaW5nVXJsIjoiaHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuYW1hem9uLmNvbS9kcC9CMDhQWkhZV0pTLz90YWc9Z2RndDBjLXAtby0xb2QtMjAiLCJjb250ZW50VXVpZCI6IjRlNTQyYzA3LTgzNmMtNDJjOS04YzQ2LWEwOWQ3N2MwZTNmZSJ9&amp;signature=AQAAAdOjv1OgwsWzm5Ci7O4q1DYqszyRc2Lgn0LknhzDbsm5&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2Fdp%2FB08PZHYWJS%2F" class="rapid-with-clickid">Apple AirPods Max 的</a>售价为 450 美元。由于这些耳罩式耳机的价格通常为 550 美元，因此等待这样的促销活动购买它们总是明智的。我们在评测中给了它们<a data-i13n="cpos:9;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/airpods-max-review-143019326.html">84 分，</a>因为它们舒适的设计、出色的音质、强大的 ANC 和良好的电池寿命。</p><p>还有很多其他<a data-i13n="cpos:10;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/best-headphones-150030794.html">无线耳机</a>比 AirPods Max <a data-i13n="cpos:11;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/best-amazon-prime-day-headphone-deals-163351574.html">更有价值</a>。然而，它们与 Apple 设备的配合效果无可比拟，这使得它们成为 Apple 生态系统中的用户的不错选择。 H1 芯片可实现快速配对和切换、免提 Siri 和其他 iOS/macOS 特定功能。</p><p><strong><em>您的 Prime 会员日购物指南</em></strong><em>：查看我们所有的</em><a data-i13n="cpos:12;pos:1" href="https://www.yahoo.com/topics/prime-day/"><em>Prime 会员日</em></a><em>报道。</em><em>在雅虎生活上</em><em>购买</em><a data-i13n="cpos:13;pos:1" href="https://www.yahoo.com/lifestyle/prime-day-2023-191047652.html"><em>最优惠的 Prime Day 优惠</em></a>。<em>关注 Engadget，了解</em><a data-i13n="cpos:14;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/amazon-prime-day-2023-124519231.html"><em>亚马逊 Prime Day 最佳科技优惠</em></a><em>。</em>在 In the Know 上<em>了解</em><a data-i13n="cpos:15;pos:1" href="htt