ully designed wearable with plenty of useful watch faces and speedy Assistant responses. Our main gripes were with the short battery life and software issues like awkward Fitbit integration — things that the upcoming launch of <a data-i13n="cpos:17;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/google-remembered-to-add-gmail-and-calendar-to-wear-os-190027384.html">Wear OS 4</a> might fix.</p><h2> Samsung Galaxy Watch 5 </h2><p><core-commerce id="19653fd9fa1a4006bdcb5bd247a4f1e3" data-type="product-list"></core-commerce></p><p>当然，Apple Watch 只能与 iPhone 配合使用。对于那些喜欢 Android 设备的人来说， <a data-i13n="elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Amazon;elmt:;cpos:18;pos:1" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;custData=eyJzb3VyY2VOYW1lIjoiV2ViLURlc2t0b3AtVmVyaXpvbiIsInN0b3JlSWQiOiI2NmVhNTY3YS1jOTg3LTRjMmUtYTJmZi0wMjkwNGVmZGU2ZWEiLCJsYW5kaW5nVXJsIjoiaHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuYW1hem9uLmNvbS9ncC9wcm9kdWN0L0IwQjJKNVRCM1E_dGFnPWdkZ3QwYy1wLW8tMW9pLTIwIiwiY29udGVudFV1aWQiOiIyMmM1OTJlMS0wNGM1LTRkNWQtODIzZi1mNDM3MWJjNmE0NTgifQ&amp;signature=AQAAAVETYTaDZwUx3oydrtYiA_SnQzNN9KsOxWtEgPrDZHBx&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2Fgp%2Fproduct%2FB0B2J5TB3Q" class="rapid-with-clickid">Galaxy Watch 5</a>是我们智能手表指南中的<a data-i13n="cpos:19;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/best-smartwatches-153013118.html">首选</a>。通常为 280 美元，目前为 160 美元，折扣 43%。三星最新的可穿戴设备运行在谷歌的 Wear OS 上，为您提供大量健康数据和健身跟踪以及睡眠指导和身体成分分析。</p><h2> Fitbit Versa 2 </h2><p><core-commerce id="9089883eb4874ad2841c444d114365d2" data-type="product-list"></core-commerce></p><p> <a data-i13n="elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Amazon;elmt:;cpos:20;pos:1" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;custData=eyJzb3VyY2VOYW1lIjoiV2ViLURlc2t0b3AtVmVyaXpvbiIsInN0b3JlSWQiOiI2NmVhNTY3YS1jOTg3LTRjMmUtYTJmZi0wMjkwNGVmZGU2ZWEiLCJsYW5kaW5nVXJsIjoiaHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuYW1hem9uLmNvbS9GaXRiaXQtRml0bmVzcy1TbWFydHdhdGNoLVRyYWNraW5nLUluY2x1ZGVkL2RwL0IwN1RXRlZEV1Q_dGFnPWdkZ3QwYy1wLW8tMW9pLTIwIiwiY29udGVudFV1aWQiOiIyMmM1OTJlMS0wNGM1LTRkNWQtODIzZi1mNDM3MWJjNmE0NTgifQ&amp;signature=AQAAAf1D2MMCTXjqREiUAyEHEcC4AEVPlgDSRjuTrQojPbSi&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2FFitbit-Fitness-Smartwatch-Tracking-Included%2Fdp%2FB07TWFVDWT" class="rapid-with-clickid">Fitbit Versa 2</a>是我们智能手表指南中的<a data-i13n="cpos:21;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/best-smartwatches-153013118.html">预算之选</a>，Prime Day 优惠价为 124 美元。 Fitbit 设备一直以健身为重点，Versa 2 跟踪并自动检测大量不同的锻炼，为您提供大量数据。但由于它是一款智能手表，因此它可以播放 Spotify，内置 Alexa，并将您的手机通知和数百个应用程序带到您的手腕上。它还与设备无关，可与 iPhone 或 Android 设备配对。</p><h2>健身追踪器</h2><h2>Fitbit 充电 5 </h2><p><core-commerce id="3ca3961339a849b186239c6fa3ea758f" data-type="product-list"></core-commerce></p><p> <a data-i13n="elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Amazon;elmt:;cpos:22;pos:1" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;custData=eyJzb3VyY2VOYW1lIjoiV2ViLURlc2t0b3AtVmVyaXpvbiIsInN0b3JlSWQiOiI2NmVhNTY3YS1jOTg3LTRjMmUtYTJmZi0wMjkwNGVmZGU2ZWEiLCJsYW5kaW5nVXJsIjoiaHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuYW1hem9uLmNvbS9kcC9CMDlCWFE0SE1CP3RhZz1nZGd0MGMtcC1vLTFvaS0yMCIsImNvbnRlbnRVdWlkIjoiMjJjNTkyZTEtMDRjNS00ZDVkLTgyM2YtZjQzNzFiYzZhNDU4In0&amp;signature=AQAAAcii-L339Tpmr7Dfew_VEJk_l6YrBQ5SnnSPgodP4e9W&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2Fdp%2FB09BXQ4HMB" class="rapid-with-clickid">Fitbit Charge 5</a>是我们 <a data-i13n="cpos:23;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/best-fitness-trackers-133053484.html">最喜欢的整体</a>智能设备，目前价格比平时低 100 美元或 50 美元。健身追踪器的功能不如智能手表那么齐全，但这通常意味着它们的电池寿命更长，而且成本更低。我们喜欢 Charge 5，因为它具有全面的活动跟踪和健康监测功能，而且外形纤薄，电池寿命长达多天。它还与 Apple 和 Android 手机配对。</p><h2> Fitbit Inspire 3 </h2><p><core-commerce id="fa924e40474a4d42ac8e5df74a64302a" data-type="product-list"></core-commerce></p